name: Informaticslab.github.com
body:
### Welcome to the InformaticsLab's github site
The CDC Informatics Lab keeps its source code repositories at this site. For more information on the Lab, please visit [http://www.phiresearchlab.org](http://www.phiresearchlab.org). For more information on the Lab's open source development tools, please visit [http://code.phiresearchlab.org](http://code.phiresearchlab.org). For more information on the Informatics Research & Development Activity, please visit [http://www.cdc.gov/osels/phsipo/irda/](http://www.cdc.gov/osels/phsipo/irda/).
### Support or Contact
You can contact the Lab via [email](mailto:informaticslab@cdc.gov) or [twitter](https://twitter.com/CDC_PHIRDL).
### Privacy
The Lab's repositories only store non-sensitive, publicly available material released under an open source license. Github.com is a third-party web application, not hosted by the CDC. All operations are subject to the CDC's Web Privacy Policy ([http://www.cdc.gov/privacy.html](available here)).
